A temporary dispensation has been applied to ST0884 version 1.1 end-point assessment plan (EPA). The dispensation removes assessment method 3: TEST from the EPA.
Knowledge statements K1,2,3,4,5,6,7 and 8 can now be assessed in assessment method 1 work based project report and presentation. For further information of mapping please use the link.
The dispensation will last from 18/12/24 until the EPA is revised.&nbsp;
If your organisation is considering beginning the delivery of this EPA, you should follow the requirements as they are detailed in the end-point assessment plan and apply the dispensation.&nbsp;
Please contact the Institute for Apprenticeships and Technical Education via enquiries.ifa@education.gov.uk should you require any further clarity.
